/target
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock
.crabcc/
.DS_Store

# Bench raw transcripts are noisy + reproducible; keep only the rendered report.
# Pattern is `*` not `/` so `!` re-includes work — git refuses to re-include a
# file whose parent directory is excluded with the trailing-slash form.
bench/results/*
!bench/results/REPORT.md
!bench/results/*.png
!bench/results/fsst-gate.md

# Research artifacts produced by sub-agents — not source.
STORAGE_RESEARCH.md
DB_*.md
crates/crabcc-core/fuzz/target/
